{"tid":374854,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇上網識另一半","createTime":"2017-08-26T05:29:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T20:03:14.000Z","uid":140379,"like":100,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6cb602d25a10416a30979aadad23e9c7f4e5d744","tid":374854,"uid":140379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:29:28.000Z","msg":"出到社會 交友圈子細<br />\n出現愈黎愈多單身狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n交友app同上網識人既數量明顯上升<br />\n當中不乏有真心交友人士 但亦好多人以網上渠道呃錢呃蝦條<br />\n大家點睇上網識人呢樣野<br />\n如果身邊好朋友同你講 佢另一半係上網識<br />\n會唔會覺得對方好怪<br />\n<br />\n覺得OK=正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得唔OK=負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7601382e4311fec42940e13b118442814ba0b347","tid":374854,"uid":73002,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:31:07.000Z","msg":"都係識人嘅其中一個渠道姐"},{"pid":"3a649b13d7381ee80fb48e6fc3022b1804819771","tid":374854,"uid":12696,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:32:53.000Z","msg":"冇基礎<br />\n好易散<br />\n經驗之談"},{"pid":"3532a7f01a93d8dc502a3b59b88ce339e820130e","tid":374854,"uid":86151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:33:06.000Z","msg":"月經"},{"pid":"5b48a1b1c83e31e9936eb5937e209fd113c0b7f9","tid":374854,"uid":83977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:05:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba6ff5ad046e764dbb005e82db22674f8d257751","tid":374854,"uid":93497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:08:47.000Z","msg":"其實如果同佢傾得埋啱話題嘅 我覺得可以有下文囉"},{"pid":"18807cbf9b028f86652b016f94dc5e30732aab8b","tid":374854,"uid":55846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:10:00.000Z","msg":"我個人覺得唔太work, 冇共同圈子已經差咁d"},{"pid":"0fe592d670dd43e7ecbf6320105351531a02b58b","tid":374854,"uid":10442,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:13:06.000Z","